listings.comment: At first I read all the comments about her work and was bit of hesitant for my website. Overal she did her job for OK. I am not impressed by work quality I experienced during the project. She lacks professionalism, takes long to answer and replies with very short messages, ignored reminders of correction on the website. I had to repeat the same thing to correction several times. She asked for extention two times. First time when she asked for extension for 7 days it was understandable, the second time I refused. She might reply here she did so becaue of I did not supply with necessary video/photo images. As I wrote above her answers took long and very short.

No complaints! Amena was always on time with deadlines, she responded quickly and even went a step further by making improvement that I had never thought of, I will rehire as soon as business picks up. she was amazing, worked honestly. I want you to try it, it will definitely not disappoint you. Thanks!

Not just working on the requirement but it is the additional recommendations which is helpful to make things easier to coordinate with her and get things done in the shortest time possible. Had a wonderful experience working with her.

Wp Amena was amazing to work with on my website redesign—solving any issues and always going the extra mile. Her attention to detail and professionalism EXCEEDED my expectations👌. Excellent communication and very responsive. Highly recommend!

We recently had the pleasure of working with Amena a fantastic web designer who truly exceeded our expectations. The level of professionalism, creativity, and attention to detail was remarkable. Our new website not only looks great but also functions seamlessly, providing a user-friendly experience that perfectly aligns with our brand. We greatly appreciated the willingness to listen to our needs and the proactive approach in offering solutions that enhanced our vision. Highly recommend for anyone looking to elevate their online presence!
